headline.main: For Migrants Headed North, the Things They Carried to the End
headline.print_headline: Things They Carried to the End

lead_paragraph: Leeds United striker Chris Wood scored twice in a 3-1 win at Birmingham City on Friday that lifted them to within one point of third-placed Huddersfield Town in the Championship.
